18 SECTION 4. AMENDATORY 57 O.S. 2021, Section 332.15, is
19 amended to read as follows:
20 Section 332.15. A. From and after the effective date of this
21 act, no member or alternate member of the Pardon and Parole Board
22 and/or or their law firm or law partners or associate may represent
23 in a legal capacity any inmate incarcerated in any state penal
24 institution. If a member or alternate member of the Pardon and
